titles.text: My name is Let√≠cia, I'm 24 years old, majoring in systems analysis and development (3rd period). Currently I work as QA at NTT DATA Brasil, being my first contact with the information technology job market. As a hobby, I study front-end development, especially vue.js.

titles.title: Work
titles.text: I work as QA, creating and running tests in API and in legacy systems, as well as the opening and closing of defects. The tools used are: Postman, SoapUI, Oracle SQLDeveloper, HPALM, MOBA and Apache Jmeter.
